sources.description:
Battledogs: A werewolf virus breaks loose in New York, prompting Major Hoffman to seek a cure while Lt. General Monning aims to create a new breed of canine soldiers.
2013.  Stars: Craig Sheffer, Dennis Haysbert, Kate Vernon

Night Of The Wild: When a massive meteor strikes a tranquil town, pet dogs turn inexplicably violent, attacking and killing the locals. Teenager Roslyn and her loyal but aging dog Shep are camping when the chaos unfolds. Separated by the turmoil and roadblocks, Roslyn and her family must reunite while battling the bloodthirsty canines before the dogs seize control of the town and escape becomes impossible.
2015.  Stars: Rob Morrow, Kelly Rutherford, Tristin Mays
